      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡价格因供应担忧缓解而维持近三周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商评估了主要种植区巴西冬季的温和天气条件以及需求疲软的风险，阿拉比卡咖啡期货交易价格接近三周来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Grifols 遭遇 4.57 亿欧元意外会计调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/grifols-new-auditor-finds-non-cash-accounting-discrepancy-linked-to-china-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年遭受做空者攻击的西班牙制药公司 Grifols SA 表示，它夸大了其在一家中国公司的股份价值，并报告了 4.57 亿欧元（4.94 亿美元）的会计调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/grifols-new-auditor-finds-non-cash-accounting-discrepancy-linked-to-china-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:53:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率决定公布前，欧洲股市因稳健数据上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因有报告显示欧元区经济上季度增长超过预期，欧洲股市上涨，投资者关注本周美国和英国央行的利率决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:22:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
